A catechisme or institution of the christen religion. Newely set forthe by Richard Tauerner Taverner, Richard, 1505?-1575.
[5], 85 [i.e. 80?], [2]+ leaves
R. Bankes], [London : Anno. M.D.XXXIX. [1539]
Place of publication and printer's name from STC. At foot of title page: Cum priuilegio, ad imprimendum solum. Signatures: A-D (-D6) E-F I-L (-L8). Imperfect; lacks leaf D6 and quire G; leaves L6 and L7 are fragments; lacks all after leaf L7; numerous misfoliations. Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
